Package io.atlasmap.v2

Class DocumentCatalog

java.lang.Object
io.atlasmap.v2.DocumentCatalog
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class DocumentCatalog extends Object implements Serializable
The Document catalog model which holds a list of DocumentMetadata for both of Source Documents and Target Documents in imported order.
